Package com.intellij.compiler

Interface CompilerReferenceService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseComponent, NamedComponent, ProjectComponent
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    CompilerReferenceServiceEx
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompilerReferenceServiceBase, CompilerReferenceServiceImpl

    public interface CompilerReferenceService
extends ProjectComponent
    The service is intended to provide an information about class/method/field usages or classes hierarchy that is obtained on compilation time. It means that this service should not affect any find usages result when initial project is not compiled or project language is not supported by LanguageCompilerRefAdapter extension. Any result provided by this service should be valid even if some part of a given project was modified after compilation.
